{%- comment -%} Shipping, Returns & Exchange policy — shared across product templates {%- endcomment -%}
<div class="pdp-policy">
  <h4 class="pdp-policy__heading">Shipping</h4>
  <ul class="pdp-policy__list">
    <li>Free shipping on all orders.</li>
    <li>A ₹100 COD (Cash on Delivery) charge applies to COD orders below ₹3,000.</li>
    <li>For international orders, customs duties may be levied at the time of delivery in certain countries.</li>
    <li>Products are shipped from our warehouse within 4 working days.</li>
    <li>Orders are delivered within 10 working days.</li>
    <li>You will receive an order tracking number as soon as we ship your order.</li>
  </ul>

  <h4 class="pdp-policy__heading">Returns</h4>
  <ul class="pdp-policy__list">
    <li>7-day return policy (returnable products only). Jewellery, socks, scarves, innerwear, masks, and items discounted 50% or more — including Mega Sale purchases — are non-returnable.</li>
    <li>Returned products must be unused, unworn, and have their original tags intact.</li>
    <li>No returns or exchanges are applicable on products purchased from the outlet sale.</li>
    <li>A non-refundable charge of ₹100 applies to all COD orders below ₹3,000. Additionally, a non-refundable charge of ₹300 applies to all COD orders for footwear.</li>
    <li>Shipping charges and COD charges are non-refundable.</li>
    <li>International orders are not eligible for return.</li>
    <li>Please share an unboxing video of the package for any wrong or missing item received.</li>
    <li>Do not hand over the product without a pick-up slip or SMS confirmation.</li>
    <li>Items purchased during a sale are non-returnable.</li>
    <li>Post-wash queries are entertained only within one month from the date of delivery.</li>
    <li>Only exchange is applicable on orders purchased on sale/offer.</li>
    <li>Only a one-time exchange is allowed.</li>
    <li>If your pin code is outside our serviceable area, you must self-ship the product via reverse logistics. (Note: your courier cost should not exceed ₹300 — we request you self-ship via “Speed Post”.)</li>
    <li>Do not accept the package if it is tampered with.</li>
    <li>All COD orders will be refunded via gift cards, as payouts are currently on hold in compliance with RBI guidelines.</li>
    <li>Do not share the OTP with the carrier if you haven’t received the product.</li>
  </ul>

  <h4 class="pdp-policy__heading">Exchange</h4>
  <ul class="pdp-policy__list">
    <li>Exchange is not available for masks, boxers, socks, and products at or below ₹899.</li>
    <li>There is no additional charge for any exchange orders.</li>
    <li>For new orders of a lower price, the balance amount will be refunded as a gift voucher.</li>
    <li>Size exchange is subject to availability.</li>
    <li>Please share an unboxing video of the package for any wrong product received.</li>
    <li>For further details, refer to our <a href="/policies/terms-of-service">Terms &amp; Conditions</a> and <a href="/pages/faq">FAQ</a>.</li>
  </ul>
</div>
